  "summary": "Learn about .PPM files and view a list of programs that open them.",
  "developer": "Jef Poskanzer",
  "how_to_open": {
    "instructions": [
      "You can open a PPM file with many image viewing and editing programs. For example, you can open a PPM file with GIMP (multiplatform), XnViewMP (multiplatform), or Netpbm (multiplatform)."
    ]
  },
  "how_to_convert": {
    "instructions": [
      "You can use Netpbm, ImageMagick or XnViewMP to convert PPM files to other image formats. For example, XnViewMP can convert PPM files to the following formats (and many others):",
      ".JPG - JPEG Image",
      ".GIF - Graphical Interchange Format",
      ".PNG - Portable Network Graphic",
      ".TIFF - Tagged Image File Format",
      ".BMP - Bitmap Image",
      ".PCX - Paintbrush Bitmap Image",
      ".TGA - Targa Graphic",
      ".JP2 - JPEG 2000 Core Image",
      ".JXR - JPEG XR Image",
      ".WEBP - WebP Image"
    ]
  },
